Heat pipe Airfoil¶

This code covers the different wrapping methods of heat pipes inside airfoils

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__delattr__(self, name, /)¶

Implement delattr(self, name).

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__dir__(self, /)¶

Default dir() implementation.

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__eq__(self, value, /)¶

Return self==value.

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__format__(self, format_spec, /)¶

Default object formatter.

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__ge__(self, value, /)¶

Return self>=value.

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__getattribute__(self, name, /)¶

Return getattr(self, name).

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__gt__(self, value, /)¶

Return self>value.

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__hash__(self, /)¶

Return hash(self).

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__init_subclass__()¶

This method is called when a class is subclassed.

The default implementation does nothing. It may be overridden to extend subclasses.

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__le__(self, value, /)¶

Return self<=value.

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__lt__(self, value, /)¶

Return self<value.

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__ne__(self, value, /)¶

Return self!=value.

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__new__(*args, **kwargs)¶

Create and return a new object. See help(type) for accurate signature.

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__reduce__(self, /)¶

Helper for pickle.

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__reduce_ex__(self, protocol, /)¶

Helper for pickle.

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__setattr__(self, name, value, /)¶

Implement setattr(self, name, value).

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__sizeof__(self, /)¶

Size of object in memory, in bytes.

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__str__(self, /)¶

Return str(self).

pyturbo.cooling.heatpipe_airfoil.__subclasshook__()¶

Abstract classes can override this to customize issubclass().

This is invoked early on by abc.ABCMeta.__subclasscheck__(). It should return True, False or NotImplemented. If it returns NotImplemented, the normal algorithm is used. Otherwise, it overrides the normal algorithm (and the outcome is cached).
